}_{-53}$ arcsec, 90\\% CL) in the case of the northwestern and western\nsubhalos. To confirm or refute these findings, high resolution space-based\nobservations extending beyond the current FF limited coverage to the west and\nnorthwestern area are essential.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jul 2015 20:00:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Dec 2015 22:03:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-27"}
