reases computing probability. Last, simulation demonstrates the feasibility\nof wirelessly powered mobile cloud computing and the gain of its optimal\ncontrol.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Jul 2015 06:15:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Mar 2016 08:23:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-14"}
